item.title: Now
item.description: November 2022 ∘ Putting my head down and finishing as many unfinished projects started this year. ∘ Completing my technical guide for ipod theming. ∘ Put all my mods into the iPod. ∘ Repair the broken Pebble watches lying around. ∘ Start my portfolio for design college. What’s Playing? ∘ Currently Reading too much manga to keep up. ∘ Currently Reading "The Dawn of Everything". ∘ Listening to How it Ends by TOLEDO.
